description: This file initializes the React application by rendering the main App component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It sets up the root rendering context and includes styling via index.css.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root React DOM element to enable the rendering of React components within a specified DOM node.

methods.name: render
methods.description: Method called on the root object to render the React component tree into the DOM.
